### Rust

```bash
cargo check
cargo test
cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings
cargo fmt --check
```

### Python

```bash
uv sync
uv run ruff check .
uv run ruff format --check .
uv run pytest -q
```

## Coding standards

- Prefer small, reviewable diffs
- No secrets in commits or logs
- Run local gates before claiming work complete
- Do **not** enable automatic Copilot code review on PRs

## PR hygiene

- Feature branch → `dev` (use `Refs #n` only)
- `dev` → `main` delivery (use `Closes #n` / `Fixes #n`)
- See `AGENTS.md` if present for fuller agent rules

